git clone https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_Python_DHT.git

sudo apt install python3-venv -y

python3 -m venv lcd_env

source lcd_env/bin/activate

nano dht_sensor.py

sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt dist-upgrade
sudo apt autoremove

python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip setuptools

sudo apt install build-essential python3-dev
sudo apt install libgpiod2

sudo apt install python3-pip python3-setuptools python3-wheel

pip install adafruit-circuitpython-dht


DHT11/DHT22 Pinout:
VCC (Pin 1) → 3.3V on Raspberry Pi (NOT 5V).
GND (Pin 2) → Ground (GND) on Raspberry Pi.
DATA (Pin 3) → GPIO pin (e.g., GPIO4) on Raspberry Pi.
NC (Pin 4) → Not connected (this is optional for most sensors).


